## Options

### Scale

Create a version of the source image which retains aspect ratio and outputs the image at a specific width (in pixels).

### Resize

Create a version of the source image with specified height and width.

### Custom sizes

Enter a set of destination sizes, separated by commas. 
A single number will scale the image to a specified width, retaining aspect ratio.
Two numbers separated by an ```x``` will generate a new image with the dimensions width x height.

